Teltoli's eyes flutter open, and she can see the two Alliance members 
following them. She grabbed one of Windlords guns and peeked over his 
shoulder from the position he was carrying her, wincing with pain.

She quickly fired four shots, countering the shots that were headed 
their way, and exploding them in mid air. She then sent two shots of 
her own back at the bots. She winced again and struggled to stay 
awake, as she could feel her vision swimming again.
